WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Spring is one of the most beautiful seasons of the year.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Trees bloom, and the weather becomes warmer.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Flowers fill the fields with vibrant colors.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Birds return and sing with joy.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:25.000
It's the perfect time to enjoy nature.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Days become longer, and the sun shines brighter.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Many people take advantage of outdoor activities.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Spring also marks the beginning of new life cycles.

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:12.000
Enjoy spring and its magic!
